  "title": "(MNC) Assistant Test Engineer|Up to $3.2k + monthly transport allowances + aws | West - LQ",
  "description": "<p>Location: Jurong east (10mins walk from JE MRT) <br />Working days: Mon - Fri, Office hours<br />Salary: Basic up to $3.2k (depending on relevant experience & education) + monthly transport allowances + AWS <br /><br />Key Duties: </p><ul><li>Carry out testing and commissioning of newly installed and modernized elevator equipment</li><li>Identify defects, perform fault analysis, and support restoration works</li><li>Assist in planning work schedules and supervising technicians</li><li>Attend to safety- and performance-related equipment issues</li><li>Support engineering improvements and technical investigations</li><li>Ensure compliance with safety, environmental, and regulatory standards</li></ul><p>Key Requirements: </p><ul><li>Min Nitec in Engineering or related field </li><li>Experience in testing, commissioning, or elevator/mechanical systems is highly advantageous</li><li>Willing to work on-site and support urgent operational needs</li></ul><p>Please submit your updated resume on Whatsapp at wa.me/6587504643 or press the APPLY NOW BUTTON.</p><p>By submitting your resume and/or personal information, you consent to the collection, use, and disclosure of your personal data by the company (or its designated agent) for the purposes of processing, administration and managing your job application.</p><p>Please be notified that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Charlotte Loh| Reg No.: R25127073</p><p>Griffin HR Consultancy Pte Ltd | EA Licence No.: 23C1449</p>",
